    "name": "Zenith Realms",
    "steam_appid": 3162120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zenith Realms is a 3D top-down cozy adventure puzzle game where Ninami embarks on an emotional journey across the fractured realms of a splintering planet. Can you help Ninami and find the way home before time runs out?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISCOVER A SPLITTING WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world that is undergoing a planetary mitosis after duplicating everything on its surface, a war had struck between the two sides  and led to the death of all but one: <strong>Ninami</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras/9f641fdb0a34cf74c97ad24ed715f316.avif?t=1748635329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras_big/9f641fdb0a34cf74c97ad24ed715f316.avif?t=1748635329 width=800 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel the tranquil yet divided landscapes of the Zenith Realms on a quest to get Ninami back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras/0e69193555178b51e8929428fb954117.avif?t=1748635329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras_big/0e69193555178b51e8929428fb954117.avif?t=1748635329 width=800 height=442 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FACE CHALLENGES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome adversaries by chasing the mischievous Raven who stole  the  gem that powers Ninami's Home portal, and learn about their shared troubled past. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras/ec6643f3c41fbe1a1b132afc87d5e061.avif?t=1748635329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras_big/ec6643f3c41fbe1a1b132afc87d5e061.avif?t=1748635329 width=800 height=442 /></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNRAVEL MYSTERIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By solving intriguing environmental puzzles, you learn more about the planetary split and explore three beautiful levels full of pre-war history, friendly creatures, and a dark secret past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras/7efe964bc190a13e28c3c181ed176a73.avif?t=1748635329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras_big/7efe964bc190a13e28c3c181ed176a73.avif?t=1748635329 width=800 height=442 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras/0e889dacf0dd8c4e64dec72c724071d9.avif?t=1748635329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162120/extras_big/0e889dacf0dd8c4e64dec72c724071d9.avif?t=1748635329 width=800 height=428 /></span></p>",
